title: Spacious rental units with two separate private rooms & bathroom for rent each
posting_body: ['“Please serious enquires only”.', 'This is a semi basement brand new built unit attached to residential home.', 'A separate entrance for privacy.', '•Two separate rooms each.', 'With large living room area for two renters only.', '* Located at Morton Grove, IL (13 min drive to O’Hare).', '(Great Location, Condition, transport, groceries and more)', 'Best of everything!', 'Unique features:', '-Fairly priced at $625 per month.', '(Shared utility bills with tenant who will be renting the other unit available).', '-Safe and friendly Neighborhood.', '-Spacious Rooms and Hardwood floors.', '-Large open style living room and Kitchen design.', '-Modern', 'Sparkling Clean units just built.', '-Oak Cabinets and Granite Counter Tops.', '-New built Bathroom with Ceramic Tiles', '-Shared Laundry in unit included.', '-Walk-in closet/Storage for whoever rent first.', '-High speed Internet available for $10 a month.', '-Street parking available.', '-As much as we love Pets, sorry no Pets at this time.', '-Any gender and background is welcome to rent the unit.', '-Strictly No smoking!', 'Tenant must be employed and responsible.', 'Minutes to the park &amp pool, all the shopping on Dempster Rd, close to Metra and between I-94 and I-294.', 'Conveniently located near grocery stores, banks, and restaurants.', "Excellent transportation at your doorstep takes you to O'Hare International Airport and to the City.", 'For more information please call via provided number 773_Four55-Six652']
